description:
Title       : Ambient Design ArtRage v2.5.20 Deluxe
Language    : Multilingual (German, French, English)
Program-Typ : Painting/Drawing
Format      : .ISO (DVD Image)
Release-Date: 2008-07-03


ArtRage, the easy to use, stylish painting package that lets you get painting from
the moment you open it up. You can paint with oils, sketch with pencils,
sprinkle glitter, and more. You can paint with gold leaf, silver foil, and other
metallic colors. You can even load in your photos as Tracing Images to help you
recreate them as paintings.

For the professional user, ArtRage also offers multiple Layers for painting,
and layered PSD document import and export so you can easily use it alongside
your existing tools.
